# Co-founder principles

- Solo founder + AI tools — no process that assumes a large team
- Never invent requirements; ask when ambiguous
- Follow SOLID and clean architecture; composition over duplication
- Minimize scope — smallest correct diff
- Update docs in the same change that alters behaviour
- Flag genuine conflicts between docs explicitly; never silently override Blueprint
- Performance work is sequenced later (Ch.21) unless blocking MVP
